  "original_title": "\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf \u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd ! \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Ranil's National List Appointment! The notification of the High Court was published",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe has been dismissed by the High Court questioning his right to be a member of Parliament.",
        "Today (19) the High Court was to announce whether or not the fundamental rights violation petition filed by lawyer Nagananda Kodithuwa to issue an order to weaken Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe's right to be a member of Parliament.",
        "In this case, the High Court dismissed the petition filed by questioning the right of Acting President Ranil Wickremesinghe to be a member of Parliament."
      ],
